Southern Cross Says It Reached Agreement on Restructuring Plans

-- B y   P e t e r   B r a n t o n
-- 
2011-09-27T09:02:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/southern-cross-says-it-reached-agreement-on-restructuring-plans.html
Southern Cross Healthcare Group Plc
said it reached agreement with its “principal landlords and
lenders” on the group’s restructuring and has started the
process of transferring its homes to new operators.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter Branton at 
 pbranton@bloomberg.net  